Strafing Breath	TYPE:General	PREFEAT:2,Flyby Attack,Flyby Breath	PREMOVE:1,Fly=1											PRETEXT:Breath weapon						DESC:You can sustain your breath weapon when you use it on the wing, convering a larger ground area in its effect.	SOURCEPAGE:p.87	BENEFIT:When you use your breath weapon while flying (either with a single move, using the flyby Attack feat, or with a double move, using the flyby Breath feat), you can extend the area covered by your breath weapon on the ground. You can use your breath weapon over a distance up to half your fly speed if you move in a straight line along that distance.
